blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: Emeralampoisottrenina Empoleon, Feraligatr, Swampert, Blastoise, Samurott, Greninja and Primarina fusion Water/Dragon Type...
caption:
Emeralampoisottrenina

Empoleon, Feraligatr, Swampert, Blastoise, Samurott, Greninja and Primarina fusion

Water/Dragon Type

Ability: Mega Torrent - 50% boost to all water moves when HP is below 50%.

Hidden Ability: Abyssal Terror - Water moves gain a 30% power boost, lowers opponent’s attack by one stage and traps them in a whirlpool.

 Stats: HP - 95, Atk - 140, Def - 110, SpA - 140, SpD - 126, Spe - 132

The Sea King Pokemon

This pokefusion was created by combining the DNA of all known water starters.  Only one has been made and for good reason; its power is too great.  It is known to be one of the biggest pokemon fusions to exist.  It currently resides deep in the depths of the ocean.  The water on its back is the source of its watery abilities and will absorb a lot of water to refill itself.  It can shoot blasts of high pressured water from the holes on its wings.  No pokemon dares to mess with it.

Reqeust for anon. I hope you like it! So, we have all these water starters here.  How are we gonna fuse them together? Make it into a dragon of course! I spent so much time on this. It’s one of the biggest sprites I have ever made.  I love this sea dragony creature! Probably one of my favourite sprites I’ve ever made. 

Don’t think I’ve ever fused 7 pokemon together before either. I suppose there’s a first time for everything!

blog.name: squidbiscuit
blog.title: ~Totally Awful All The Time~
blog.description:
Devon, She/Her, Asexual, In a state of sustained fear.
I draw stuff. Blog features material that is almost always tagged appropriately unless I mess something up. 
Commissions are currently [closed] and I do not schedule when they re-open so I cannot give you a time frame for that. Askbox is usually open for doodle suggestions,headcanons, questions, what have you. 
READ BEFORE SENDING MESSAGES!
_Please only suggest things for fandoms I have shown recent interest in. I don't plan out my interests so questions about old fandoms and if I plan to draw for them are not appreciated. I am NEVER looking for new fandoms to get into, please DO NOT suggest new series for me, I promise you I HAVE heard already, I'll mention it on my own if I care. 
FEMALE FOCUS KINK ART IS BY COMMISSION ONLY AND NOT APPRECIATED WHEN SUGGESTED!!!
 ABSOLUTELY NO PERSONAL KINK STORIES! I am massively uncomfortable with irl fetish stories from people.
Even tho I am marked as an NSFW blog I do not enjoy sex based suggestions and would appreciate if you didn't leave them. I do not like pregnancy based kinks at all and I will not draw them or discuss them.Don't ever end a message in "Thanks in advance" because I will not draw for it under implied obligations.
I am not here to teach you the intricacies of my sexuality. If you do not understand it do your own basic research instead of violating the privacy of a complete stranger. I am not my kink, do not treat me as a character.
